<section class="sidebar">
    {{#if loggedIn}}
    <p>Click on a restaurant to see its details and add/change its rating.</p>
    <h2>More Options</h2>
    <button class="sidebar-btn" id="add-restaurant">Add A Restaurant</button>
    <button class="sidebar-btn" id="add-restaurant">Change My Password</button>
    <button class="sidebar-btn" id="add-restaurant">Log Out</button>
    <script src="/js/create.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/update-user.js"></script>
    {{!-- no need to add script for logout.js here, since it's conditionally added on main.handlebars --}}
    {{else}}
    <div>
        <h2>Sign Up</h2>
        <form class="signup-form">
            <div>
                <label for="username-signup">Username:</label>
                <input type="text" id="username-signup" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="password-signup">Password:</label>
                <input type="password" id="password-signup" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <button type="submit" class="sidebar-form-btn" id="signup-btn">Sign Up</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2>Log In</h2>
        <form class="login-form">
            <div>
                <label for="username-login">Username:</label>
                <input type="text" id="username-login" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="password-login">Password:</label>
                <input type="password" id="password-login" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <button type="submit" class="sidebar-form-btn" id="login-btn">Log In</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    {{!-- no need to add script for login.js here, since it's conditionally added on main.handlebars --}}
    {{/if}}
</section>
<main>
    {{#if loggedIn}}
    <h2>
        My To-Dine List
    </h2>
    <div class="filter">
        {{!-- add filter code here --}}
    </div>
    <div class="restaurant-list">
        {{#each restaurants as |restaurant|}}
        <div class="restaurant">
        {{!-- will need to add CSS to make div.restaurant change on hover so it's clearly a link --}}
            {{> restaurant-info restaurant}}
            <h3>{{restaurant.name}}</h3>
            <img src="/img/{{restaurant.imgName}}.jpg" class="restaurant-card-img">
            {{!-- will need to add imgName key to each imported restaurant object with filename of associated image --}}
            {{#if ratingCheck}}
            {{!-- add code for rating stars based on rating here --}}
            {{!-- could add separate keys for stars 1, 2, and 3 with conditional emtpy or full star icon --}}
            {{!-- will need to add ratingCheck key to each imported restaurant object with value of false if no rating --}}
            {{else}}
            <p>I haven't rated this restaurant</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
    {{!-- add scripts to edit restaurant on click here --}}
    {{else}}
    <p>What was the name of that restaurant your friend has been telling you to try? And did
        you try the new sushi place a couple weeks ago or the one across town?</p>

    <p>You’ve got enough on your plate already. Let us keep track of your restaurant list so
        you can just worry about what you’re going to order.</p>

    <p>Make a To-Dine List and filter it by cuisine when you need help deciding where to go.
        Once you’ve visited a restaurant, give it a rating so you know to go back.</p>

    <p class="red">Create an account or log in to the left to get started.</p>
    {{/if}}
</main>